name: bio-embeddings-bepler
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "bio-embeddings-bepler" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/bio_embeddings_bepler-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fa8a6351414709d208e6b41852e73bf4f0afd5cbde5896ff4fc647cc57aa51cc

build:
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 2
  skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - cython
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - {{ pin_compatible('numpy') }}
    - pytorch

test:
  imports:
    - bepler
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/bio-embeddings-bepler/
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: 'Bepler model for bioembeddings'
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hadim
